OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Santa's poorly'           
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Falternative festive ad goes
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fviral                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An alternative Christmas advert which  
OL,6, portrays a bereaved father struggling  
OL,7, to make Christmas special for his son  
OL,8, has gone viral on social media.        
OL,10,FThe video, entitled The GoKart, was    
OL,11,Fshot by a team of young videographers  
OL,12,Fin West Yorkshire and has attracted    
OL,13,Fmillions of views.                     
OL,15,FFilmmaker Sam Teale, 20, said they     
OL,16,Fwanted to create something that        
OL,17,Freflected the cost of living crisis.   
OL,19,FThe message is "Christmas is made, not 
OL,20,Fbought", he said.                      
